BFN 

  [Text] The Democratic Republic of Yemen [DRY] has welcomed 
the resolution taken by the Security Council on Yemen. It 
announced its agreement and preparedness to comply with its 
operating chapters. The DRY also announced in a message to Dr. 
Butrus Butrus-Ghali, the UN secretary general, its readiness to 
receive the fact-finding commission which will be dispatched and 
do its best to assist it and facilitate its mission. 

